      propertyPath: m_text
      value: There was a sudden spike in hospitalizations in the past few days for
        sudden high fevers. It was soon discovered by doctors that the WTH virus
        had evolved into a new strain. Doctors warn people to stay cautious and vax-up,
        since being vaccinated helps lower your chances of infection and could help
        lessen the severity of it. Scientists are now working developing a new WTH
        vaccine to combat this strain.
