    - target: {fileID: 2159534897854115432, guid: 21826f423699bc441b9766e15ba0be68, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: While the roll-out of the WTH vaccine has been largely successful, trust
        in vaccines and in turn, scientists have fallen. The panic and chaos of the
        outbreak led to high emotions, so people became reactive even to the littlest
        news and side effects. It is now the task of the doctors, scientists and
        the like to rebuild this trust and assure people on the dependability and
        use of vaccines.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
